Tirada guud ee cudurka Corona Virus (COVID-19) ee ka dhacay Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday 1da Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020
Tirada guud ee kiisaska cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay muujineysaa isbeddelo la mid ah dalalka Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, iyagoo xaqiijinaya in inkasta oo ay ku jirto marxalad kala duwan iyadoo ku xiran waddanka, masiibada COVID-19 ay si dhakhso leh ugu sii socoto wadamada oo dhan.
Iyada oo la raacayo khibrada Talyaaniga, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha caafimaadka ee wadamada waa inay u diyaariyaan si ka sii badan faafitaanka bukaanka qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel iyo, ugu muhiimsan, daaweyn degdeg ah.
Bishii Diseembar 31, 2019, tiro ka mid ah kiisaska cudurka sanbabada ee aan la aqoon waxay ka soo baxeen Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Bishii Janaayo 9, 2020, Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa ku wargelisay in kiiska uu yahay coronavirus cusub, oo hadda loo yaqaan 'coronavirus 2 of severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS-CoV-2).
Tan iyo markaas, cudurka ka dhasha cudurka SARS-CoV-2 waxaa loo yaqaan cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19).
caddaynta ilaa iyo hadda waa in 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 ay ku dhacaan cudur fudud, taas oo ah cudur neefsashada oo leh ama aan lahayn cudurka sanbabada, inta badanna way soo kabsadaan.
Qiyaastii 14% kiisaska, COVID-19 waxay u gudubtaa cudur aad u daran, oo u baahan cusbitaal, halka 6% kiisaska haray ay u gudubto cudur aad u daran, oo u baahan daaweyn degdeg ah.
Dhimashada bukaanka isbitaalka ah ee COVID-19 waa 4%.
Daraasaddan waxaan ku qiimeynay isbeddellada ku saabsan heerarka guud ee COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EU/EEA) iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, waxaanan isbarbardhignay kuwa ka jira gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignay tirada hadda jirta ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka Midowga Yurub/ECE iyo Boqortooyada Midowday iyo kuwa Talyaaniga intii u dhaxaysay Janaayo 31 iyo Maarso 15, 2020.
Kiisaska COVID-19 ee wadamada EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Shiinaha kadib, COVID-19 ayaa ku faafay dhulka, iyo xawaaraha cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 ee adduunka intiisa kale ayaa hadda raacaya waddankaas.
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, agaasimaha guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa COVID-19 ku dhawaaqay cudur faafa.
Daabacaadda 5-ta Maarso ee Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. ayaa soo sheegtay kiisaskii ugu horreeyay ee la xaqiijiyay ee COVID-19 ee Yurub, sida ku cad qeexitaanka kiiska WHO.
Midowga Yurub/Ebees, saddexda kiis ee ugu horreeya ee la xaqiijiyay ayaa waxaa soo warramay Faransiiska 24ka Janaayo 2020 dadka ka soo laabtay Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Laga soo bilaabo 15 Maarso 2020, kiisaska COVID-19 ayaa la ogaaday dhammaan 30da dal ee EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, iyadoo laga bilaabo 31ka Diseembar 2019 ilaa taariikhda kor ku xusan, 39,768 kiis iyo 1,727 dhimasho ayaa la soo sheegay, iyadoo 17,750 kiis iyo 1,441 dhimasho ay ka dhaceen Talyaaniga oo keliya.
Hel tirada guud iyo tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19
Xarunta Yurub ee Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (ECDC) tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee laga soo sheegay waddan kasta oo adduunka ah, oo laga helo kaliya ilo rasmi ah sida Wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee wadamada, mas'uuliyiinta caafimaadka ee qaranka iyo gobolka iyo WHO, ayaa la cusbooneysiiyay maalin kasta 8ka subaxnimo.
Macluumaadkan waxaa loo adeegsaday in lagu qiimeeyo isbeddellada COVID-19 ee Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, loona barbardhigo kuwa Talyaaniga.
Marka la soo dhawaado heerka cudurka COVID-19 ee jira, waxaan xisaabinay 14 maalmood oo dhacdooyin COVID-19 ah oo isku dhafan, taas oo tixgelineysa horumarka dabiiciga ah ee COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo Midowga Yurub/EES iyo Boqortooyada Midowday intii u dhaxaysay Janaayo 1 ilaa Maarso 15, 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada guud ee kiisaska la soo sheegay ee waddan kasta ilaa 15 Maarso 2020 saacaddii 8 subaxnimo, waxaanan isbarbardhignay Talyaaniga intii u dhaxaysay 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Isbeddellada COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Isbeddellada 14 maalmood ee COVID-19 ee ku soo kordha wadamada Midowga Yurub/Ebees iyo Boqortooyada Midowday guud ahaan waxay raacday kuwa ka socda gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha (Tilmaanta 1).
Guud ahaan, EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, dhacdada COVID-19 ee isku dhafan waxay bilaabeen inay kordhaan qiyaastii Febraayo 21 waxayna si weyn u kordheen, ka dibna qiyaastii Febraayo 28, 2020 (waxyaabo dheeri ah).
Tani waxay ugu horreyntii sabab u ahayd kororka degdegga ah ee kiisaska laga soo sheegay Talyaaniga, laakiin dhammaan waddamada kale ee EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday waxay muujiyeen isbeddelo isku mid ah oo kor u kaca heerarka COVID-19 (waxyaabo dheeri ah).
Muuqaalka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday marka loo eego Talyaaniga muddadii 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Waxa uu tilmaamay in saacadaha 8 galabta ee 15ka Maarso 15 dal oo kale oo ka tirsan EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ay soo bandhigeen tirada guud ee kiisaska la midka ah kuwa Talyaaniga 3 toddobaad ama ka yar ka hor.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay tilmaamayaan in tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee la soo sheegay ay si degdeg ah u kordhayaan Midowga Yurub/Eheeg iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Isbeddellada la arkay ee ku saabsan heerarka guud ee COVID-19 waxay muujinayaan in masiibada ay ku sii socoto xawaare isku mid ah wadamada oo dhan.
Tani waxay dhacdaa inkasta oo wadamada ay ku jiraan marxalado kala duwan, isbeddellada ku yimaada tallaabooyinka nidaamyada caafimaadka dadweynaha ee qaranka, iyo suurtagal ahaan qeexitaanno kala duwan oo kiisaska ah ee wadamada iyo borotokool kala duwan oo loogu talagalay xulashada bukaanka la tijaabiyo xaqiijinta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan tijaabinta cusboonaysiinta.
Bilowgii bishii Maarso ee sanadka 2020, dhakhaatiirta gobollada ay saameysay ee Talyaaniga waxay ku tilmaameen xaalad ay ku baahanyihiin 10% bukaannada qaba COVID-19 daaweynta sare, warbaahinta ayaa sheegtay in isbitaalada iyo xarumaha daaweynta sare ee gobolladaasi ay horeyba u gaareen awoodooda ugu badan.
Xogta ku saabsan cusbitaalka iyo/ama ICU ee COVID-19 ee ku jira xaaladaha gudaha ayaa hadda laga heli karaa heerka EU/EEA oo kaliya 6% iyo 1% xaaladaha, siday u kala horreeyaan (ma muuqato xogta).
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waa in si nidaamsan loo ururiyaa si loo daro xogta kormeerka ee hadda jirta iyadoo diiradda la saarayo tirada kiisaska la soo sheegay iyo tirada dhimashada.
Daraasad la sameeyay 2010-2011 ayaa muujisay isbeddel weyn oo ku yimid helitaanka sariiraha ICU iyo kuwa semi-dheer ee Yurub, laga bilaabo 29.2 sariirood ee Jarmalka illaa 4.2 sariirood ee Portugal 100 000 qof kasta.
Taas macnaheedu waa in dalalka ay yeelan karaan ilo ka yar ama ka badan Talyaaniga (12.5 sariirood oo ICU ah iyo daaweyn nus-dheer oo loogu talagalay dadweyne 100,000 ah intii u dhaxaysay 2010 iyo 2011).
Sawirada la qaabeeyay ee la xiriira buuxinta awoodda nidaamka caafimaadka, oo leh qiyaasooyin ku saabsan waddan kasta oo EU/EEA ah iyo Boqortooyada Midowday oo ku saabsan heerka cudurka COVID-19 ee la isugu jira halis ka badan 90% awoodda sariirta daryeelka caafimaadka ee, waxaa lagu bixiyaa cusbooneysiinta lixaad ee qiimeynta degdegga ah ee ECDC ee COVID-19.
Maaddaama kiisaska ay ilaa hadda ku badan yihiin gobollada qaar ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha daryeelka degdegga ahna ay caadi ahaan adeegaan dadweyne go'an oo gobol ahaan ku baahsan, macluumaadka ku saabsan kiisaska iyo sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah waxaa ugu horreyn la heli karaa Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistical Purposes 2 (NUTS-2).
Tusaale ahaan Talyaaniga iyo isbeddellada dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in masiibada COVID-19 ay si dhakhso leh ugu sii socoto Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha caafimaadka ee waddanka waa in ay diyaar garoobaan xaalad gudbinta bulshada ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo kororka tirada bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad, gaar ahaan daryeel degdeg ah, sida ka dhaca gobollada ay saameysay Talyaaniga.
Sida lagu muujiyey qiimeynta halista degdegga ah ee ECDC, habka degdegga ah, hanti-dhaqanka ah iyo dhammaystiran ayaa muhiim u ah in la daahiriyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2, iyadoo la beddelayo habka xakamaynta ilaa habka yareynta, maadaama kororka degdegga ah ee la filayo in kiisaska la kordhiyo uusan siin karin waqti ku filan go'aan-qaadayaasha iyo isbitaalada si ay u fahmaan, u aqbalaan oo u qaabeeyaan tallaabooyinkooda si ku habboon haddii aan horay loo hirgelin.
Qiimaynta halista degdegga ah waxay sidoo kale liis gareysaa tallaabooyinka caafimaadka dadweynaha ee lagu yareynayo saameynta cudurka faafa.
Waxaa jira fursad yar oo ay dalalku fursad u helaan inay xoojiyaan dadaalkooda xakamaynta si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyo in la yareeyo cadaadiska nidaamka caafimaadka.
Haddii ay guuldareystaan dadaalladaas, nidaamyada caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee EU/EEA waxay u badan tahay inay jiraan cudurro bukaan ah oo u baahan daaweyn degdeg ah maalmaha ama usbuucyada soo socda.
Cudurka cudurka coronavirus ee 2019 (COVID-19), oo ay sababtay cudurka coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ee cudurka neefsashada daran ee daran (SARS), ayaa u geeriyooday in ka badan 3,000 oo qof, waxaana uu ku dhacay in ka badan 80,000 oo qof Shiinaha iyo adduunka intiisa kale, taas oo keentay masiibo dadka.
Sida uu u eg yahay fayraska SARS-CoV, oo sababiyay SARS kumanaan qof sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ayaa sidoo kale laga yaabaa in laga faafiyo garaaca waxayna sababi kartaa calaamado la mid ah hab la mid ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, COVID-19 waxay leedahay halis iyo dhimashada ka yar SARS, laakiin waa mid aad u faafa, waxayna saameyn badan ku yeelataa dadka waayeelka ah marka loo eego dhalinyarada, raggana way ka badan yihiin dumarka.
Iyadoo jawaab u ah kororka degdegga ah ee daabacaadda cudurka cusub, maqaalkan wuxuu doonayaa inuu bixiyo qiimeyn hadda iyo dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan ujeeddada cilmi baarista, taas oo si degdeg ah u horumarsan.
Waxaan ka hadli doonaa mabaadi'da aasaasiga ah ee cudurka, etiology, virology, cudurka, daaweynta, saadaasha iyo ka hortagga cudurka.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli u baahan yihiin jawaab, waxaan rajeyneynaa in daraasaddan ay ka caawiso fahamka iyo baabi'inta cudurkan cadowga ah.
Bandhigga gu'ga ee 25ka Janaayo 2020 wuxuu noqday xusuus gaar ah oo aan la iloobin dhammaan Shiinaha oo lagu qasbay inay ku xayiran yihiin fasaxa oo dhan iyo dhowr toddobaad oo soo socda sababo la xiriira cudurka faafa ee fayraska cusub.
Fayraska wuxuu u eg yahay coronavirus (CoV) oo sababay cudur faafa oo ah cudurka neefsashada daran ee SARS (SARS) sanadkii 2003; sidaa darteed waxaa loo magacaabay SARS-CoV-2 Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) Febraayo 11, 2020, cudurkaas oo la xiriira waxaa loo magacaabay cudurka COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay Wuhan ee Shiinaha, wuxuuna si deg deg ah ugu faafay dalka oo dhan iyo ku dhawaad 50 dal oo kale oo adduunka ah.
Ilaa 2da Maarso 2020, fayraska ayaa sababay in ka badan 80,000 oo kiis oo COVID-19 ah oo la xaqiijiyay, in ka badan 40,000 oo bukaan ah ayaa soo kabsaday iyo in ka badan 3,000 oo bukaan ah oo dhintay.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay "cadowga dadweynaha ugu weyn", waxaana laga yaabaa inuu ka awood badan yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood, in ka badan 200 oo maqaal ayaa lagu daabacay COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan virology, epidemiology, etiology, diagnostics, iyo daaweynta, tan iyo warbixinta ugu horreysa ee Janaayo 7, 2020, oo go'aamisay kala-soocida fayraska ka soo jeeda bukaanno badan.
Maqaalkani wuxuu doonayaa inuu soo koobo horumarka cilmi baarista ee ku saabsan aaggan cusub ee horumarinta degdegga ah.
Marka ay khuseyso, waxaan isbarbardhigi doonaa COVID-19 sida SARS iyo cudurka kale ee COVID, oo ah cudurka neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, 2012).
Waxaan sidoo kale ka wada hadli doonaa wixii aan hadda ka baranay ka hortagga iyo saadaasha cudurka iyo arrimaha kale ee degdegga ah.
CoVs waxaa caadi ahaan loo tixgeliyaa inay yihiin cudur-darrada aan u dhimanayn dadka, waxayna sababaan ugu horreyn qiyaastii 15% qabowga caadiga ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee qarnigii la soo dhaafay, waxaan laba jeer helnay cudurrada aadka u nugul ee COVID ee aadanaha, kuwaas oo ah SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, kuwaas oo sababi jiray cudur faafa oo ka dhashay Shiinaha 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya 2012 siday u kala horreeyaan, oo dhawaan u faafay dalal kale oo dhowr ah oo leh cudur iyo dhimasho cabsi badan.
Sidaa darteed, COVID-19-ka hadda jira waa cudurka COVID-ka ee saddexaad ee taariikhda aadanaha ee la diiwaangeliyey.
Sida lagu muujiyey sawirka 1.1, 1 waxaa markii ugu horreysay lagu soo sheegay Wuhan 31kii Diseembar 2019 kiisaska cudurka sanbabada ee aan la aqoon.
