Intaa waxaa dheer, ilaalinta dheelitirka elektrolyticka, ka hortagga iyo daaweynta cudurrada labaad iyo qaraxa septicka, iyo ilaalinta howlaha xubnaha muhiimka ah ayaa sidoo kale muhiim u ah bukaannada qaba SARS-CoV-2.
Cytokine cascade waxaa loo yaqaanaa inay ka dhalato falcelinta daran ee nidaamka difaaca ee bukaanka qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Cytokine cascade waa qaab ka mid ah jawaabta caabuqa ee nidaamka, oo lagu garto inay sii deynayso tiro ka mid ah cytokines, oo ay ku jiraan TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
cytokines-yada ayaa keena in unugyada nidaamka difaaca jirka ay sii daayaan tiro badan oo xagjirka ah, kuwaas oo ah sababta ugu weyn ee SDRA iyo dhaawaca xubnaha badan.
Difaacida difaaca jirka waa mid muhiim u ah daaweynta biyo-dhaca cytokine, gaar ahaan bukaannada culus.
Kortikosterooyida iyo tocilizumab, oo ah anti-IL6 antibody, ayaa loo isticmaalaa daaweynta cascade cytokine.
Daaweynta kale ee difaaca difaaca ee loo yaqaan ' cytokine cascade ' waxaa ka mid ah qaabeynta jawaabta difaaca ee T-ka; xannibaadda IFN-y, IL-1 iyo TNF; ka hortagga JAKs, blinatumomab; suppressor 4 cytokine signal; iyo HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids sida immunosuppressants ayaa si weyn loo isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo halista waxyeelada caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, qiyaasta sare ee steroids ma aysan faa'iido u lahayn dhaawaca sanbabada ee daran ee bukaanka qaba SARS iyo COVID-19.
