Horumarinta tallaal badbaado leh oo wax ku ool ah oo looga hortago SARS-CoV-2 dadka aan la difaacin cudurka ayaa ah hawl degdeg ah oo muhiim u ah xakamaynta cudurka faafa ee hadda jirta.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waa dhibaato in la gudbo dhibaatada, sababtoo ah muddada dheer (celcelis ahaan 18 bilood) ee loo baahan yahay in la horumariyo tallaal iyo isbeddellada ku yimaada awoodda COVID.
Sida cudur cusub, COVID-19 ayaa hadda bilaabay inay muujiyaan horumarka caafimaad ee buuxda, waxayna gaadhay kumanaan bukaan ah.
