Si kastaba ha ahaatee, SARS-CoV ayaa la sheegay in la gudbiyo marka bukaanku si xun u xanuunsadaan, iyadoo inta badan gudbinta aysan dhicin marxaladda bilowga ah.
Sidaa darteed, cudurka COVID-19 ee hadda jira waa mid aad uga daran oo aad uga adag in la xakameeyo sida cudurka SARS.
