Calaamado badan ayaa xaqiijinaya in dhammaan HCoVs ay ka soo jeedaan dufanka, halkaasoo fayrasyada ay si fiican u habboon yihiin oo aan cudur-darrada ahayn, laakiin ay muujiyaan kala duwanaansho weyn oo hidde-wadaag ah.
