Ka hor inta aan la goyn nooca B814 ee HCoV-229E ee cudurka hargabka ee bukaanka qaba hargabka caadiga ah, COVID-19 kala duwan ayaa laga goynayay xoolaha qaba cudurka, oo ay ku jiraan digaagga, jiirka, lo'da, doofaarka, bisadda iyo eyga.
Tobankii sano ee la soo dhaafay, toddoba HCoVs ayaa la aqoonsaday.
