Russel Zimmerman oo ah agaasimaha fulinta ee ururka ganacsatada Australia ayaa sheegay in ganacsatada ay isku dayaan in ay kordhiyaan kaydka, laakiin in xaddidaadaha golaha deegaanka ee ku saabsan inta jeer ee gaarsiinta baabuurta ay ka dhigaan mid adag.
