Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku dhawaaqay in COVID-19 uu yahay cudur faafa
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa sheegay Arbacadii in cudurka COVID-19 ee hadda jira ee loo yaqaan 'SARS-CoV-2' uu yahay cudur faafa.
Inkastoo erayga "dhibcaha" uu tilmaamo kaliya heerka cudurku faafayo, mana aha sida khatarta ah ee kiisaska gaarka ah ay yihiin, WHO waxay ku adkeysay baahida loo qabo in dawladuhu ay wax ka qabtaan:
Wadamada oo dhan wali way beddeli karaan wadada masiibada.
Haddii dalalku ay awoodaan inay ogaadaan, tijaabiyaan, daaweeyaan, go'doomiyaan, raad raacaan oo ay dadka u soo ururiyaan jawaab, ayuu yiri Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, agaasimaha guud ee WHO.
Waxaan aad uga walaacsan nahay heerarka cabsida leh ee faafitaanka iyo culeyska iyo heerarka cabsida leh ee aan waxqabad lahayn.
Dr. Tom Frieden oo ah agaasimaha hore ee Xarumaha Xakamaynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurrada ee Mareykanka ayaa sheegay in ay tahay masiibad "aan horay loo arag".
