Kaliya dadka reer Koonfur Afrika ee baaritaankaasi taban yahay ayaa dib loo soo celiyay.
Natiijooyinka tijaabada ayaa sii daayay dhammaan dadka reer Koonfur Afrika, oo ay ku jiraan shaqaalaha duulimaadka, duuliyeyaasha, shaqaalaha hoteelka, booliska iyo askarta ku lug leh howlgalka bini'aadamnimada kuwaas oo, sidii tallaabo ka hortag ah, lagu hayo daawashada iyo karantiil muddo 14 maalmood ah Resort The Ranch.
Bishii Maarso 20aad, Mareykanka ayaa bilaabay inuu ciidamadiisa qayb ahaan ka soo baxo Ciraaq masiibada awgeed.
5 Febraayo, Wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibadda ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in 21 dal (oo ay ku jiraan Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad & Tobago, Masar iyo Iran) ay caawimaad u diraan Shiinaha.
Ardayda Shiinaha ee Jaamacadaha Mareykanka ayaa isugu yimid inay caawiyaan inay gargaar u diraan dadka ku dhaca fayraska Shiinaha, koox wadajir ah oo ku nool aagga Great Chicago ayaa la sheegay inay ku guuleysteen inay 50,000 oo maaskaro N95 ah u diraan isbitaalada Gobolka Hubei bishii Janaayo 30. Ururka gargaarka bini'aadamka ee Direct Relief, oo iswaafajinaya FedEx, ayaa 200,000 maaskaro wajiga ah iyo qalab kale oo ilaalin shaqsiyeed oo ay ku jiraan gacmo-qabasho iyo dabool, u diray gaadiidka hawada ee degdegga ah Isbitaalka Wuhan Union bishii Janaayo 30.
Febraayo 5, Bill iyo Melinda Gates waxay ku dhawaaqeen deeq dhan $100 milyan oo doolar oo ay ugu deeqeen WHO si ay u maalgeliyaan cilmi baarista tallaalka iyo dadaallada daaweynta, iyo sidoo kale ilaalinta "dadka halista ku jira Afrika iyo Koonfurta Aasiya".
Interaksyon ayaa sheegtay in dowladda Shiinaha ay bishii Febraayo 6 ay 200,000 oo maaskaro ah ugu deeqday dalka Filibiin kadib markii Senator Richard Gordon uu 3.16 milyan oo maaskaro ah u diray Wuhan.
Febraayo 19, Laanqeyrta Cas ee Singapore waxay ku dhawaaqday inay Shiinaha u dirayso $2.26 milyan oo kaalmo.
Japan waxay Wuhan ugu deeqday hal milyan oo maaskaro, Turkiga waxay u dirtay qalab caafimaad, Ruushka wuxuu u diray in ka badan 13 tan oo alaab caafimaad oo loo helo Wuhan, Malaysia waxay ku dhawaaqday inay ugu deeqdo 18 milyan oo gacmo gacmeedyada caafimaad Shiinaha, Jarmalka wuxuu u dhiibay alaab caafimaad oo kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan 10,000 oo dharka ilaalinta, Mareykanka wuxuu u deeqay Shiinaha 17.8 tan oo alaab caafimaad ah wuxuuna ballanqaaday in uu ku daray 100 milyan oo doolar oo dheeraad ah oo ah kaalmo dhaqaale ah dalalka ay saameysay. Ka dib markii kiisaska Shiinaha ay xasilloon yihiin, waddanku wuxuu sii wadaa inuu caawiyo caalammo badan oo ay saameysay masiibada.
Bishii Maarso Shiinaha, Cuba iyo Ruushka ayaa u diray alaab caafimaad iyo khabiiro si ay uga caawiyaan Talyaaniga inay maamusho cudurka Coronavirus.
Ganacsade Jack Ma wuxuu u diray 1.1 milyan oo qalab tijaabada ah, 6 milyan oo waji-xidh ah iyo 60,000 oo dharka difaaca ah Addis Abeba ee Itoobiya si ay ugu qaybiyaan Midowga Afrika.
kadib wuxuu Panama u diray 5,000 oo qalab tijaabada ah, 100,000 oo waji-xidh ah iyo 5 dabayl.
