Tani ma aha calaamad wanaagsan oo ah in ay tahay mid aad u wanaagsan oo ah wadajirka Yurub".
Bishii Maarso 22, kadib markii uu taleefan la qaatay Ra'iisul Wasaare Giuseppe Conte, Madaxweynaha Ruushka Vladimir Putin wuxuu diyaariyey ciidanka ciidanka Ruushka si ay u diraan dhakhaatiirta ciidanka, gawaarida cudur-demmista gaarka ah, iyo qalab kale oo caafimaad oo Talyaaniga ah.
