Bishii Febraayo 11, 2020, baaritaanka waxaa diiwaangeliyey Adeegga Farsamada Caafimaadka ee Federaalka. Bishii Maarso 12, 2020, Mayo Clinic waxay sheegtay inay soo saartay baaritaan lagu ogaanayo cudurka COVID-19. Bishii Maarso 13, 2020, Roche Diagnostics waxay heshay oggolaansho FDA ah oo loogu talagalay baaritaan lagu sameyn karo 3.5 saacadood oo ballaaran, taas oo u oggolaanaysa mashiinka inuu ka baaraandego qiyaastii 4,128 baaritaanno 24 saacadood gudahood.
Bishii Maarso 19, 2020, FDA waxay u soo saartay Ogolaanshaha Isticmaalka Degdegga ah (USA) shaybaarada Abbott si ay u tijaabiyaan nidaamka m2000 ee Abbott; FDA waxay horay u soo saartay oggolaansho Hologic, LabCorp, iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
21 Maarso 2020 Cepheid waxay sidoo kale heshay US FDA tijaabada oo qaadanaysa 45 daqiiqo.
