Laga bilaabo Maarso 2020, American College of Radiology waxay ku talineysaa in "TC aan loo isticmaalin screening ama tijaabada ugu horreysa ee lagu ogaado COVID-19". Laga soo bilaabo Maarso 2020, CDC waxay ku talineysaa PCR baaritaanka bilowga ah.
