Ilaa hadda ma jirto wax muujinaya in isticmaalka antiseptics ama jeermis-demmista lagu taliyey ay keeni karto xulashada jirrada u adkaysta antibiyootikada dabiiciga ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee saabuunada bakteeriyada waxay ku jiraan wakiilo bakteeriyo caadi ah sida triclosan, taas oo leh liis ballaaran oo ka mid ah noocyada jirka ee u adkaysta.
Markaa, xitaa haddii noocyada antibiotic-ka difaaca aan la dooran saabuunada bakteeriyada, waxaa laga yaabaa inaysan waxtar u lahayn sida ay u sheegaan.
Marka laga reebo surfactants iyo wakiilada ilaalinta maqaarka, qaababka adag waxay ku jiri karaan aashidooyin (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) sida pH-ga xakameynaya, benzoic acid oo antimicrobial ah, iyo qoyaan kale oo maqaarka (aloe vera, fitamiinada, mentol, qaansheegta dhirta). falanqayn dhamaystiran oo ka socota Jaamacadda Oregon School of Public Health ayaa muujisay in saabuunada caadiga ah ay u waxtar badan yihiin ka hortagga cudurada iyo ka saarista bakteeriyada gacmaha sida saabuunada bakteeriyada ka hortagga ee loo yaqaan 'antibacterial soaps' ee loogu talagalay macaamiisha ugu dambeeya ee ku jira triclosan.
Biyaha kulul ee gacmaha lagu dhaqdo si raaxo leh uma kulmaan si ay u dilaan bakteeriyada.
Bakteeriyada ayaa koraya si dhakhso badan heerkulka jirka (37 oC).
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, biyo kulul oo saabuun leh ayaa ka waxtar badan biyo qabow oo saabuun leh si looga saaro saliida dabiiciga ah ee haysta wasakhda iyo bakteeriyada.
Si ka duwan sida dadku u aaminsan yihiin, daraasadaha sayniska ayaa muujinaya in biyo kulul aysan waxtar u lahayn yareynta culeyska microbial ee gacmaha.
Qalabka nadaafadda gacmaha ama antisepticka waa wakiil nadaafadeed oo gacmaha ka soo baxa oo aan biyo lahayn.
Dhamaadkii 1990-meeyadii iyo bilowgii qarnigii 21aad, wakiilada nadaafadda gacmaha ee aan biyo lahayn ee ku saleysan khamriga (oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan alaabada nadaafadda gacmaha ee khamriga, alaabta nadaafadda gacmaha ee antiseptic, ama nadaafadda gacmaha) ayaa bilaabaya inay caan ka noqdaan.
Inta badan waxaa lagu sameeyaa isopropyl alcohol ama ethanol oo lagu sameeyay walxaha qallalan sida carbomer (polymer ama acrylic acid) oo lagu sameeyo gel, ama humidifier sida glycerin, oo lagu sameeyo dareere ama foom si loo fududeeyo isticmaalka iyo in la yareeyo saameynta qalajinta khamriga.
Ku darista hydrogen peroxide waxay kordhisaa waxqabadka bakteeriyada. gacmaha nadiifiya ee ugu yaraan 60 ilaa 95% khamri ku jira waxay si wax ku ool ah u dilaan bakteeriyada.
Daawooyinka caafimaadka ee khamriga ku saleysan waxay dilaan bakteeriyada, bakteeriyada badan ee u adkaysta (MRSA iyo VRE), cudurka hargabka, iyo qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada (oo ay ku jiraan HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, tallaalka, hargabka iyo hepatitis) iyo fangaska.
Qalabka nadiifinta khamriga ah ee leh 70% khamri ayaa dila 99.97% (hoos u dhigma 3.5 logarithms, oo la mid ah hoos u dhigista 35 decibels) bakteeriyada gacmaha 30 ilbiriqsi ka dib markii la isticmaalo iyo 99.99% ilaa 99.999% (hoos u dhigma 4-5 logarithms) bakteeriyada gacmaha 1 daqiiqo ka dib marka la isticmaalo.
Qalabka nadiifinta gacmaha ee khamriga ku saleysan ayaa ku dhowaad gebi ahaanba aan waxtar lahayn fayraska nooca Norovirus (ama Norwalk), oo ah sababta ugu badan ee cudurka cudurka cudurka qaba.
Dhabarka iyo gacmaha, fartaada iyo dhamaadka, ku dhufo qiyaastii 30 ilbiriqsi ilaa dareeraha, foomka ama gelku ay qalalaan.
Sidoo kale faraha waa in si fiican loo maydhaa, iyadoo la isku qodayaa labada gacmood. Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurrada waxay ku talineysaa in gacmaha lagu maydho nadaafadda gacmaha, gaar ahaan marka gacmaha ay muuqdaan kuwo wasakh ah.
