Tani waa mid ka mid ah khadadka cilmi baarista sayniska ee hadda la qaatay si loo horumariyo daaweyn ammaan ah oo wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay COVID-19.
Tilmaamaha kale ee cilmi baarista waxaa ka mid ah horumarinta isku darka plasma iyo tallaalka COVID-19. SARS-CoV-2 waxay leedahay qiyaastii 66 borotiinooyin oo la isku daro, mid kasta oo leh dhowr barta isku xirnaanta.
Falanqaynta dhibcaha xiriirkaas waxay bixisaa qorshe macquul ah oo lagu horumarinayo daroogada antiviral ee wax ku oolka ah ee ka dhanka ah borotiinka COVID-19.
Qaar ka mid ah borotiinka ugu muhiimsan ee SARS-CoV-2 waxaa ka mid ah protease-ka la midka ah papain, RNA-ka ku xiran RNA polymerase, helicase, protein S, iyo ADP ribofosfatase.
Hussein A. A., et al., wuxuu bartay dhowr xeryood oo codsade ah oo uu markii dambe hagaajinayay oo falanqeeyay isbarbardhigga qaab dhismeedka ee daawooyinka la oggolaaday ee ugu badan si loo dardar geliyo horumarinta daawo awood leh oo ka dhan ah SARS-CoV-2 daraasaddiisa hore ee loo taliyey naqshadeynta daraasad caafimaad.
Chloroquine waa daawo ka hortagta maleriya oo sidoo kale loo isticmaalo cudurrada difaaca jirka.
Bishii Maarso 18aad, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine la xiriira ay ka mid noqon doonaan afar daawood oo lagu bartay qayb ka mid ah tijaabada caafimaad ee Solidarity.
Guddoomiyaha gobolka New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka loo yaqaan 'cloroquine' iyo 'hydroxychloroquine' ee gobolka New York ay bilaaban doonaan Maarso 24.
Daaweynta looma oggola nidaamka tijaabada caafimaad ee FDA waxaana loo oggol yahay EU-da oo kaliya in lagu tijaabiyo daaweynta degdegga ah ee bukaanka isbitaalka ah ee aan heli karin daaweynta tijaabada caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "isticmaalka, qiyaasta ama muddada loo qaato hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga ama daaweynta cudurka SARS-CoV-2" aysan weli la aasaasin.
Dhakhaatiirta ayaa sheegay inay isticmaalayaan daroogada marka "aan jirin ikhtiyaar kale".
Magaalada Istanbul koox cilmi baaris oo Turki ah ayaa wadata daraasad yar oo ku saabsan isticmaalka chloroquine marka la daro zinc, vitamin A, vitamin C iyo vitamin D.
Waxbarashooyin waaweyn ayaa ka socda Jaamacadda Duke iyo Jaamacadda Oxford.
Dugsiga caafimaadka ee NYU Langone wuxuu wadaa tijaabo ku saabsan badbaadada iyo waxtarka isticmaalka horumarinta hydroxychloroquine.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee Shiinaha ee Wuhan iyo Shenzhen ayaa sheegay in ay muujiyeen in favipiravir uu ahaa mid "oo si cad waxtar u leh".
Shenzhen, 35 bukaan ayaa helay baaritaan taban afar maalmood gudahood celcelis ahaan, halka 45 bukaan oo aan helin jirada ay jirada u qaadeen 11 maalmood.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay Wuhan oo ay ku lug lahaayeen 240 bukaan oo qaba cudurka sanbabada, kala badh ayaa la daaweeyey favipiravir, kala badhna waxaa la siiyey umifenovir.
Hay'adda dawooyinka ee Talyaaniga ayaa dadka u sheegtay in caddaynta la heli karo ee ku salaysan daawada ay tahay mid yar oo hordhac ah.
Bishii Abriil 2, Jarmalka ayaa ku dhawaaqay in ay Japan ka iibsan doonto daawooyinka si ay u keydiso, isla markaana ay ciidanka u isticmaali doonto si ay u gaarsiiso isbitaalada jaamacadaha, halkaas oo loo isticmaali doono in lagu daaweeyo bukaannada qaba COVID-19.
Sida laga soo xigtay South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe ayaa u abuurtay furfurnaan maamulka Trump ee ku saabsan iibsashada daroogada. Daawada ayaa laga yaabaa inay ka yar tahay waxtarka kiisaska daran ee cudurka marka fayraska uu horay u soo kordhay.
Isticmaalka waxaa laga yaabaa inaanay ahayn mid ammaan u ah haweenka uurka leh ama haweenka isku dayaya inay uurka qaataan.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay lopinavir/ ritonavir (Kaletra), oo ah isku darka lopinavir iyo ritonavir antivirals, ayaa lagu ogaaday in "ma jirto wax faa'iido ah oo la arkay".
Daawooyinka waxaa loo sameeyay in lagu horjoogo HIV-ka inuu soo laabto iyada oo loo marayo isku xirnaanta protease.
Koox cilmi baareyaal ah oo ka tirsan Jaamacadda Colorado ayaa isku dayaya inay beddelaan daawooyinka si ay u helaan xeryahooda ku xiran protease-ka SARS-CoV-2. Waxaa jira dhaleeceyn ka jirta bulshada sayniska ku saabsan in la wareejiyo kheyraadka si loo soo celiyo daawooyinka si gaar ah loogu soo saaray HIV/AIDS.
WHO waxay lopinavir/ritonavir ku dartay tijaabada caalamiga ah ee Solidarity.
Remdesivir waxaa abuuray oo ay horumarisay Gilead Sciences sidii daaweyn loogu talagalay cudurka fayraska Ebola iyo cudurrada fayraska Marburg. Gilead Sciences waxay ogaatay in remdesivir uu leeyahay waxqabad antiviral in vitro oo ka dhan ah fiilo, pneumo, paramix iyo coronavirus.
Dhibaatooyinka ka mid ah daaweynta antiviral waa difaac u yeelashada mutaasyada, taas oo keeni karta cudurro daran ama faafa.
Daraasado hore oo la sameeyay ayaa sheegaya in remdesivir uu leeyahay xannibaad sare oo hiddaha u ah difaaca jirka. Waxaa jira tijaabooyin caafimaad oo dhowr ah oo socda, oo ay ku jiraan labo ay sameeyeen Isbitaalada Jaamacadda Cleveland, midna dadka qaba cudur dhexdhexaad ah iyo mid kale kuwa qaba cudur daran.
