Tallaalka COVID-19 waa tallaal la filayo oo looga hortago cudurka coronavirus ee 2019 (COVID-19).
Inkastoo aysan jirin tallaal tijaabooyin caafimaad oo la dhammeystiray, waxaa jira dadaalo badan oo socda si loo horumariyo.
Dhamaadkii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa sheegay in aysan filaynin in tallaal looga hortago SARS-CoV-2, oo ah fayraska cudurka u horseeda, uu heli karo wax ka yar 18 bilood.
Shan qof oo codsanaya tallaalka ayaa ku jiray wajiga koowaad ee daraasadaha ammaanka bishii April.
COVID-19 waxaa la ogaaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
Waxaa dhacay faafitaan ballaaran oo ka dhashay cudurka 2020ka, taas oo horseeday maalgashiyo iyo cilmi baaris aad u badan oo loogu talagalay horumarinta tallaalka.
Ururo badan ayaa isticmaalaya genomes la daabacay si ay u horumariyaan tallaal laga yaabo in laga hortago SARS-CoV-2.
Tallaabada Ururka Isku-darka ee Cudurka Faafa ee CEPI ayaa bishii Abriil sheegtay in baahida loo qabo horumarinta tallaalka ay yihiin xawaaraha, awoodda wax soo saarka, horumarinta baaxadda weyn iyo helitaanka caalamiga ah.
Bishii Abriil, cilmiga CEPI waxay soo sheegeen 10 barnaamij oo tiknoolajiyad kala duwan ah oo la cilmi baarinayo lana horumarinayo bilowgii sanadka 2020 si loo abuuro tallaal wax ku ool ah oo ka dhan ah COVID-19.
Hadafka barnaamijyada ugu waaweyn ee ka soo horjeeda daraasadaha amniga wajiga 1 waxaa ka mid ah:
nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA) (horumarinta marxaladda I iyo codsadaha tallaalka: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virus vector (horumariye wajiga 1 ah iyo codsade tallaal: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus vector nooca 5)
Sida ay shaaciyeen saynisyahannada CEPI bishii April, wadar ahaan 115 codsade oo tallaal ah ayaa ku jira marxaladaha bilowga ah ee horumarinta, 78 ka mid ahna waxaa la xaqiijiyay inay yihiin mashaariic firfircoon (79, sida laga soo xigtay Machadka Milken). 37 kale ayaa la shaaciyay laakiin macluumaad yar ayaa loo heli karaa dadweynaha (oo la tixgeliyo ama la qorsheynayo).
Tijaabada marxaladda I-II waxay sameeyaan baaritaan caafimaad iyo difaaca jirka, sida caadiga ah waxay ku dhacdaa randomized, placebo-ka iyo multicentric, iyadoo la go'aamiyo qiyaaso sax ah oo wax ku ool ah.
Tijaabada wajiga 3 waxay inta badan ku lug leeyihiin dad badan oo ka tirsan kooxda xakamaynta. Waxay tijaabiyaan waxtarka tallaalka ka hortagga cudurka, iyadoo ay la socdaan saameynta xun ee qiyaasta ugu fiican.
79 codsade oo ah kuwa ugu horeeya ee tallaalka horumarinta (oo la xaqiijiyay horaantii Abriil 2020), 74 ayaa wali aan la tijaabin dadka (waxay sii wadaan cilmi baarista hore).
Janaayo 24, 2020, Jaamacadda Queensland ee Australia ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay baaraneyso suurtagalnimada tallaal leh xarig molekular ah, kaas oo si genetically ah u beddeli kara borotiinka fayraska si ay u kiciso falcelin difaaca.
Bishii Janaayo 24, 2020, Xarunta Caalamiga ah ee Tallaallada (VIDO-InterVac) ee Jaamacadda Saskatchewan waxay ku dhawaaqday in la bilaabay shaqooyinka tallaal, iyada oo ujeedadu tahay in la tijaabiyo dadka sanadka 2021.
Mashruucyada horumarinta tallaalka ayaa lagu dhawaaqay Xarunta Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada Shiinaha, Janaayo 26, 2020, iyo Jaamacadda Hong Kong, Janaayo 28.
Bishii Janaayo 29, 2020, Shirkadaha Dawooyinka Janssen, oo uu hogaaminayo Hanneke Schuitemaker, ayaa ku dhawaaqay inay bilaabeen shaqooyinkooda horumarinta tallaalka.
