Markii uu ka bilowday Wuhan, Shiinaha, fayraska iyo cudurka waxaa loo yaqaan "coronavirus" iyo "Wuhan coronavirus".
Bishii Janaayo 2020 ayaa WHO waxay ku talisay "2019-nCov" iyo "2019-nCoV cudurka neefsashada ee degdegga ah" inay ahaadaan magacyo ku meel gaar ah oo loogu talagalay fayraska iyo cudurka, sida ku cad tilmaamaha 2015 ee ka dhanka ah isticmaalka goobaha magaca cudurka iyo fayraska.
