Tallaabooyinka tijaabada ah ee mid kasta oo ka mid ah istaraatiijiyadahaas waa in la tijaabiyaa badbaadada iyo waxtarka. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka ayaa laga bilaabay afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku sugan Seattle.
Tallaalka ayaa ku jira koodhka hiddaha ee aan waxyeelayn ee laga soo nuqul ka dhigay fayraska cudurka keena.
In ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad ayaa socda tan iyo bishii Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa qiimeeyay daaweyntii la oggolaaday ee cudurka malariyada, oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Dib u habeynta daroogada antiviral ayaa ka kooban cilmi baarista ugu badan ee Shiinaha, iyadoo sagaal tijaabooyin caafimaad oo marxaladda III ah ee remdesivir ah ay ka sameeyeen dalal badan, sida warbixin la soo saaray dhamaadka Abriil.
Falanqaynta dhaqdhaqaaqa horumarinta caafimaad ee codsadayaasha daawada iyo tallaalka COVID-19 ayaa socotay bishii Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo kale oo antiviral ah ayaa lagu qiimeynayaa daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo lagu daro interferon beta.
Waxaa jira isku day lagu xaqiijinayo waxtarka remdesivir tan iyo bishii Maarso 2020.
Horumar caafimaad ayaa lagu arkay bukaanka la daaweeyay remdesivir isticmaalka naxariista.
Tijaabooyinka heerka 3aad ee caafimaad ayaa lagu wadaa Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaalay daaweynta malariyada, ayaa lagu daraaseeyay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, iyadoo natiijooyin hordhac ah la helay.
