Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay oggolaansho isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine marka loo eego dhakhaatiirta daaweynta dadka qaba COVID-19. Daabacaadda 7aad ee tilmaamaha Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ka mid ah interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si loo isticmaalo COVID-19.
Xogta hordhaca ah waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo ribavirin ah loo baahan yahay si loo joojiyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitasoxanide waxaa lagu talinayaa in lagu daraaso in vivo ka dib markii ay muujisay heer hoose oo ka hortag ah oo SARS-CoV-2. Daraasadaha ayaa muujiyay in borotiinka bilowga ah ee ku jira diyaarinta serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo la adeegsanayo ACE2 receptor.
Daraasadaha ku saabsan chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo leh ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaado waaweyn oo ka hortagay bulshada caafimaadka inay qaataan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasado dheeraad ah. Oseltamivir ma xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana laha wax shaqo ah oo la yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa dhibaato marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine uu leeyahay sifooyinka ka hortagga duufaanka cytokine. Tocilzumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta ee Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Tijaabada aan la kala soocin ee heer qaranka ee heerka labaad ee Talyaaniga ayaa socda, kadib markii ay muujisay natiijooyin wanaagsan dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Marka la isku daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee ferritin serum si loo ogaado duufaanta cytokine, waxaa la filayaa inay baabi'iso horumarkaasi, kuwaas oo loo arko inay sabab u yihiin dhimashada dadka qaar ee saameeyay.
Cudurka interleukin-6 ee loo yaqaan 'interleukin-6 receptor antagonist' ayaa FDA-da ansixisay iyadoo la raacayo daraasadaha kiiska dib u eegista ee daaweynta cudurka 'steroid-refractory cytokine-release syndrome' ee sabab ka duwan, CAR T-cell therapy, sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo la xakameyn karo oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo muujinaya in tocilzumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
